{"tid":1731526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】只有非中國國籍人士先可以搵領事保護","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T17:53:21.000Z","uid":32204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe0ee38f39da3879238d6a384ba02ceff80b056","tid":1731526,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"我喺上一個 post 發現好多人唔了解點解 BNO / BC 甚至其他國籍搵領事幫唔到手<br />\n<br />\n已確認BNO係垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1731440/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1731440/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n其實根據 《國際聯合會國籍法公約》<br />\n第4條<br />\n國家關於本國人民之兼有他國國籍者對於該第二國不得施外交上之保護。<br />\n<br />\n即係話唔理你拎咩國籍，只要你仲係有中國國籍，領事都唔會幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家要向領事求救真係最好搵外國人，除非你冇中國國籍<br />\n<br />\n仲有大家唔好再水 BNO 去叫求命<br />\n依加仲係 BNO 身份嘅基本上都係有中國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d0c76b4b8f7a0130331e46fa9245c3a75d046","tid":1731526,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af959cc7b35805468f83a73903f8552e3654a8c4","tid":1731526,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"大家有其他國籍真係死都要搵方法退支那國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6bc66dfa6d227afcfb4378b2b9a74ce8b6b13b","tid":1731526,"uid":332860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}